# .codeqlignore — tells the CodeQL extractor (during `database create`) which

## paths to skip entirely.  This stops CodeQL's own bundled Python scripts from

## being extracted into the database and then reported as findings

## ---

## Syntax is identical to .gitignore

## CodeQL CLI and language-pack Python scripts (index.py, python_tracer.py, …)

.tools/

## Compiled CodeQL database — never project source

.codeql-db/

## Python virtual environment managed by uv

.venv/

## Coverage and cache artefacts

htmlcov/
.mypy_cache/
.ruff_cache/
.pytest_cache/
__pycache__/
